<h2>Changelog</h2>
<h4>08/10/2018 - 0.17</h4>
<ul>
    <li>Allow setting limit of posts</li>
    <li>Add issue post type</li>
</ul>
<h4>20/09/2018 - 0.16</h4>
<ul>
    <li>Fix RSVP crash</li>
    <li>Allow filtering on post types on the list</li>
    <li>Save post-types in user account, if available</li>
    <li>Proper storage of syndication targets</li>
    <li>Allow delete action in post list and update screen</li>
    <li>Experimental support for q=source (see Settings)</li>
</ul>
<h4>16/09/2018 - 0.15</h4>
<ul>
    <li>Fix sending a file to media endpoints</li>
    <li>Support for rendering repost</li>
    <li>Basic support for updating posts (see Settings)</li>
</ul>
<h3>10/09/2018 - 0.14</h3>
<ul>
    <li>Cleaner date formatting in timeline</li>
    <li>Check required fields on post types</li>
    <li>Cleaner positioning of 'new'</li>
    <li>Send post status (published or draft)</li>
    <li>Fix uploading portrait images</li>
</ul>
<h3>08/09/2018 - 0.13</h3>
<ul>
    <li>Support for media endpoint</li>
    <li>Add maximum image size settings</li>
    <li>Syndication targets are now saved via ?q=config</li>
    <li>Get around a missing account preference</li>
</ul>
<h3>07/09/2018 - 0.12</h3>
<ul>
    <li>Fix crash on Lollipop</li>
</ul>
<h3>06/09/2018 - 0.11</h3>
<ul>
    <li>Allow sending location</li>
    <li>More lighter styling and cleaner icons</li>
    <li>Add counter on all bodies</li>
    <li>Use custom tabs for external link</li>
</ul>
<h3>10/08/2018 - 0.10</h3>
<ul>
    <li>Use indigenous.abode.pub for authentication</li>
    <li>Detect connection when trying to post or read channels</li>
    <li>Better styling of micropub overview screen</li>
    <li>A lot of cleanup in code</li>
</ul>
<h3>10/06/2018 - 0.9</h3>
<ul>
    <li>Allow multiple accounts</li>
    <li>Set focus on title for bookmark and reply when URL is prefilled</li>
    <li>Check photo mimetype for compressing</li><li>Get syndication targets on login</li>
    <li>Ignore h-card types in reader</li>
    <li>Add image settings</li>
    <li>Add changelog</li>
</ul>
<h3>22/04/2018 - 0.8</h3>
<ul>
    <li>Create events and allow RSVP</li>
    <li>Allow to configure the like/share/repost/reply intents in the share screen</li>
    <li>Pull to refresh for channels and timelines</li>
    <li>Various bug fixes and some cleaning in channels</li>
</ul>
